# across C, C++, Rust, Go, Python, JavaScript, Haskell, C#, Java, Kotlin, Lua
# =============================================================================

# ======================
# OS & Desktop
# ======================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

